+# EDTS VIN Configuration Resolver
+
+Production VIN workflow for EDTS (**DT-D067**). Official NHTSA vPIC only.
+
+```bash
+cd edts-vin-resolver
+npm install
+npm run vin -- 1HTKHPVK8KH805188
+```
+
+See [`docs/VIN_RESOLVER_SPEC.md`](docs/VIN_RESOLVER_SPEC.md) and [`docs/VIN_RESOLVER_RUNBOOK.md`](docs/VIN_RESOLVER_RUNBOOK.md).
+
+**Honesty:** Creates configuration **candidates**, not verified digital twins.
